This is the code which fails with `NullPointerException`:
```
  public static void init() {
    EnvironmentContext.put(EnvironmentContext.ENGINE_NAME, "flink");
    EnvironmentContext.put(EnvironmentContext.ENGINE_VERSION, FlinkPackage.version());
  }
```

`FlinkPackage.version()` calls this method to get the version number:
```
DataStream.class.getPackage().getImplementationVersion()
```

Maybe an issue with the classpath?

